            <p>We have a lot of exciting training drills for absolute beginers. Beginers are exposed to basketball shooting drills like the form shooting, Kevin Durant shooting workout, wing screen, Ray Allen shooting, Stephen Curry shooting, player decision shooting and spot fast break shooting. </p>
        </div>
