            <h3>Intermediate</h3>
            <p>We have a lot of exciting training drills for intermediate hoopers. This set of hoopers are drilled with offensive moves like the overlap, 1v1 moves, euro finishing, baseline escape, trailing lay up and dribbling drills </p>
        </div>
        <div class="training-col">
            <h3>Expert</h3>
            <p>We have a lot of exciting training drills for absolute hoopers. Our hoopers are drilled with layup and finishing drills, rebounding drills, agility or defense drills, passing drills, dribbling drills, post play drills, warm up drills, conditioning drills and footwork drills.</p>
